# BPM System — Role × Module Access Matrix

> **Public Assets & Facilities Management (BPM)**
> Quezon City Government | 14 Roles · 6 Modules + Admin

---

## 🏛️ Module Overview

| # | Module | Description |
|---|--------|-------------|
| **M1** | ⚰️ Cemetery & Burial | Burial applications, niche management, indigent assistance, death records |
| **M2** | 🌳 Parks & Recreation | Park venue reservations, usage logs, booking calendar |
| **M3** | 🏘️ Barangay Facility | Facility reservations, approvals, ordinances, constituent records |
| **M4/5** | 💧 Water & Drainage | Service tickets, leak reports, installations, connection requests |
| **M6** | 📦 Asset Inventory | Property tracking, ocular inspections, inventory reports |
| **💳** | Payments & Finance | Transaction reconciliation, official receipts, revenue reports |
| **⚙️** | System Admin | User management, audit logs, office/employee master data |

---

