## 🎯 Access Level Legend

| Symbol | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| ✅ Full | Complete read/write/approve access to entire module |
| 🔶 Partial | Specific actions only (role-scoped) |
| 📝 Apply only | Citizen self-service — submit & view own records |
| — | No access |

---

## 📊 Role Count by Module

| Module | Roles with Access |
|--------|:-----------------:|
| ⚰️ Cemetery & Burial | 4 (Cemetery Office, SSDD, Death Reg, Citizen) |
| 🌳 Parks & Recreation | 2 (Parks Admin, Citizen) |
| 🏘️ Barangay Facility | 4 (Secretary, Punong, Desk Officer, Citizen) |
| 💧 Water & Drainage | 3 (Utility Eng, Helpdesk, Citizen) |
| 📦 Asset Inventory | 2 (CGSD, FAMCD) |
| 💳 Finance / Payments | 3 (Treasurer, Cemetery Office, Citizen) |
| ⚙️ System Admin | 1 (System Admin only) |
